sect3.synopsis:
array(  key =>  value
     , ...
     )
// 键（key）可是是一个整数 integer 或字符串 string
// 值（value）可以是任意类型的值

sect3.example:
    类型强制与覆盖示例


<?php
$array = array(
    1    => "a",
    "1"  => "b",
    1.5  => "c",
    true => "d",
);
var_dump($array);
?>


    &example.outputs;


array(1) {
  [1]=>
  string(1) "d"
}




     上例中所有的键名都被强制转换为 1，则每一个新单元都会覆盖前一个的值，最后剩下的只有一个
     "d"。

混合 integer 和 string 键名
<?php $array = array( "foo" => "bar", "bar" => "foo", 100 => -100, -100 => 100, ); var_dump($array); ?>
&example.outputs;
array(4) { ["foo"]=> string(3) "bar" ["bar"]=> string(3) "foo" [100]=> int(-100) [-100]=> int(100) }

    没有键名的索引数组


<?php
$array = array("foo", "bar", "hallo", "world");
var_dump($array);
?>


    &example.outputs;


array(4) {
  [0]=>
  string(3) "foo"
  [1]=>
  string(3) "bar"
  [2]=>
  string(5) "hallo"
  [3]=>
  string(5) "world"
}

仅对部分单元指定键名
<?php $array = array( "a", "b", 6 => "c", "d", ); var_dump($array); ?>
&example.outputs;
array(4) { [0]=> string(1) "a" [1]=> string(1) "b" [6]=> string(1) "c" [7]=> string(1) "d" }
可以看到最后一个值 "d" 被自动赋予了键名 7。这是由于之前最大的整数键名是 6。

    访问数组单元


<?php
$array = array(
    "foo" => "bar",
    42    => 24,
    "multi" => array(
         "dimensional" => array(
             "array" => "foo"
         )
    )
);

var_dump($array["foo"]);
var_dump($array[42]);
var_dump($array["multi"]["dimensional"]["array"]);
?>


    &example.outputs;


string(3) "bar"
int(24)
string(3) "foo"

sect3.synopsis:
$arr[key] = value;
$arr[] = value;
// key 可以是 integer 或 string
// value 可以是任意类型的值

sect3.note:

     这并不意味着总是给键名加上引号。用不着给键名为常量或变量的加上引号，否则会使 PHP
     不能解析它们。





<?php
error_reporting(E_ALL);
ini_set('display_errors', true);
ini_set('html_errors', false);
// Simple array:
$array = array(1, 2);
$count = count($array);
for ($i = 0; $i < $count; $i++) {
    echo "\nChecking $i: \n";
    echo "Bad: " . $array['$i'] . "\n";
    echo "Good: " . $array[$i] . "\n";
    echo "Bad: {$array['$i']}\n";
    echo "Good: {$array[$i]}\n";
}
?>



    &example.outputs;


Checking 0: 
Notice: Undefined index:  $i in /path/to/script.html on line 9
Bad: 
Good: 1
Notice: Undefined index:  $i in /path/to/script.html on line 11
Bad: 
Good: 1

Checking 1: 
Notice: Undefined index:  $i in /path/to/script.html on line 9
Bad: 
Good: 2
Notice: Undefined index:  $i in /path/to/script.html on line 11
Bad: 
Good: 2

sect2.example:
   集合


<?php
$colors = array('red', 'blue', 'green', 'yellow');

foreach ($colors as $color) {
    echo "Do you like $color?\n";
}

?>


   &example.outputs;


Do you like red?
Do you like blue?
Do you like green?
Do you like yellow?

   在循环中改变单元


<?php
// PHP 5
foreach ($colors as &$color) {
    $color = strtoupper($color);
}
unset($color); /* ensure that following writes to
$color will not modify the last array element */

// Workaround for older versions
foreach ($colors as $key => $color) {
    $colors[$key] = strtoupper($color);
}

print_r($colors);
?>


   &example.outputs;


Array
(
    [0] => RED
    [1] => BLUE
    [2] => GREEN
    [3] => YELLOW
)

   下标从 1 开始的数组


<?php
$firstquarter  = array(1 => 'January', 'February', 'March');
print_r($firstquarter);
?>


   &example.outputs;


Array 
(
    [1] => 'January'
    [2] => 'February'
    [3] => 'March'
)
